description: Praised for its initial response to the pandemic, the Czech Republic is now preparing for the worst.
title: Covid-19: How the Czech Republic's response went wrong
title_page: Covid-19: How the Czech Republic's response went wrong - BBC News
maintext: "It's really disappointing. I've felt very angry at times. Because all of the effort from springtime just seems to have gone down the drain. The virus is still here, and things have gone pretty badly since then," she told the BBC.
